{"id": 7849, "source": "pestle", "subject": "chemistry", "course": null, "level": "SL", "paper": "1", "year": "2020", "session": "20N", "subtopic": "4-3-covalent-structures", "title": "20N.1.SL.TZ0.10", "topic_id": "4", "source_url": "https://pestle.pages.dev/app/", "question_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Which molecule is most polar?</span></p>\n<p>A.  <math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>CHF</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></math></p>\n<p>B.  <math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>CF</mi><mn>4</mn></msub></math></p>\n<p>C.  <math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>CClF</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></math></p>\n<p>D.  <math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>CCl</mi><mn>4</mn></msub></math></p>\n</div>", "solution_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>A</p>\n</div>", "examiners_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>63% of the candidates could identify CHF<sub>3</sub> as more polar than CClF<sub>3</sub>. A surprising number selected either CCl<sub>4</sub> or CF<sub>4</sub> as the most polar.</p>\n</div>"}